Stephen Fry becomes latest celebrity to quit Twitter
Fry has joined Mastodon, an alternative social network, which has seen a surge in users since Musk’s takeover.

In his first message, or “toot” on Mastodon, he said: “I wonder if this service [is] named after the great confession of Bertie Wooster’s: ‘As a rule, you see, I’m not lugged into Family Rows. On the occasions when Aunt is calling Aunt like mastodons bellowing across primeval swamps . . . the clan has a tendency to ignore me.’ ”
